des:
This Alexa skill was created by Montour Middle School 8th graders as a reference for fellow students that will be starting high school next year. The skill is updated regularly, so check back soon if your answer is not addressed the first time!

Montour’s mission is to provide an exemplary and comprehensive educational experience that enables each individual to achieve maximum potential, to respect themselves and others, and to become a responsible and productive citizen.
